<br>
Thanks for reading this, I know NOTHING about xml .. <br>
<br>
I was wonderinging if the following sounds good? Its what im REALLY looking for in a Player window.<br>
<br>
Text example below:<br>
<br>
Player first name curHP / maxHP<br>
-------- Line or Blank line<br>
Player HP bar HP% / PetHP %<br>
Pet HP bar (combined on same bar as Player HP?)<br>
Mana Bar mana %<br>
Air Bar Air %<br>
-------- Line or Blank line<br>
AC: ac% WT: weight% XP: xp% AAxp: aaxp%<br>
-------- line or Blank line<br>
Button ....... Button ......... Button ............ Button<br>
Pet Attack .. Pet Backoff .. Pet Guardhere .. Pet Guardme<br>
<br>
